form_title.ms_form_title_llm_v1: Contact any social security office immediately if you:, Form OA-702 ( (5-80)

full_text: Contact any social security office immediately if you: lose your card-to - get a duplicate card. change your name - to get a card in your new name. are unable to work because of a severe disability expected to last a year or more. are 62 or older- - to ask about retirement checks are within 2 or 3 months of age 65, even if you don't plan to retire - to sign up for Medicare. Department of Health and Human Services Social Security Administration Form OA-702 (5-80)
